OL,3,C'Revolutionary' new robot shrinks
OL,4,Cwaiting times for endometriosis surgery
OL,6,FGynaecologists at Southmead Hospital
OL,7,Fin Bristol say a surgical robot which
OL,8,Fhelps doctors to remove endometriosis
OL,9,Fis "revolutionising" patient care.
OL,11,FThe machine - which allows doctors to
OL,12,Foperate using robotic arms - has
OL,13,Falready been used in surgeries on 400
OL,14,Fendometriosis patients.
OL,16,FIt's believed an additional 144
OL,17,Fpatients will be treated every year
OL,18,Fwith the new technology, which doctors
OL,19,Fsay makes surgery less invasive and
OL,20,Fleaves patients with shorter recovery
OL,21,Ftimes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
