OL,3,C'Revolutionary' new robot shrinks
OL,4,Cwaiting times for endometriosis surgery
OL,6,F"Since introducing robotics we have
OL,7,Fmade tremendous improvements to our
OL,8,Fwaiting lists," said Jessica Preshaw,
OL,9,Fconsultant gynaecologist at Southmead
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,F"Robotic surgery is quicker, and what
OL,13,Fthat means is you can complete more
OL,14,Fsurgical cases within one day."
OL,16,FEndometriosis is a condition which
OL,17,Fsees tissue similar to the lining of
OL,18,Fthe womb grow on other organs like the
OL,19,Fovaries, bladder and bowel, as well as
OL,20,Fthe diaphragm and pelvis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
