OL,3,C'Revolutionary' new robot shrinks
OL,4,Cwaiting times for endometriosis surgery
OL,6,FJoanne Forbes suffered debilitating
OL,7,Fpain caused by endometriosis for 20
OL,8,Fyears before she was operated on using
OL,9,Fthe robot.
OL,11,F"I'd often have to stay in bed, maybe
OL,12,Fcrawl my way to the bathroom at
OL,13,Ftimes," she said.
OL,15,F"The pain just became so bad, the
OL,16,Fperiods were so bad, despite me being
OL,17,Fon contraception to try and stop them.
OL,18,FIt disabled my life."
OL,20,FHow has the robot changed surgery?
