OL,3,C'Revolutionary' new robot shrinks
OL,4,Cwaiting times for endometriosis surgery
OL,6,FSouthmead Hospital is one of only four
OL,7,Fhospitals in the UK with a dedicated
OL,8,Frobot for gynaecological surgery.
OL,10,FThe machine enables surgeons to
OL,11,Fprecisely remove diseased tissue from
OL,12,Fa patient's organs while sitting down
OL,13,Fat a console.
OL,15,FConventional laparascopic - or keyhole
OL,16,F- endometriosis surgery requires
OL,17,Fsurgeons to stand with outstretched
OL,18,Farms, for up to five hours at a time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
