OL,3,C'Revolutionary' new robot shrinks
OL,4,Cwaiting times for endometriosis surgery
OL,6,FIn that case, the tools are limited to
OL,7,Fvertical and horizontal movements,
OL,8,Fwhereas the grips controlling the
OL,9,Frobot can move in a full 360-degree
OL,10,Farc, giving the surgeon more
OL,11,Fmanoeuvrability.
OL,13,FIslam Gamaleldin, another consultant
OL,14,Fgynaecologist at the hospital, said
OL,15,Fconventional keyhole surgery can often
OL,16,Fbe exhausting.
OL,18,F"If you're mentally fatigued there's a
OL,19,Fchance that you might do something or
OL,20,Fcause a problem," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
