OL,3,C'Revolutionary' new robot shrinks
OL,4,Cwaiting times for endometriosis surgery
OL,6,F"With the robot it just takes this
OL,7,Faway from you. You're sitting down,
OL,8,Fyou're relaxed, and you can come off
OL,9,Fthe console, walk around the theatre a
OL,10,Flittle bit to relax, then come back to
OL,11,Fit."
OL,13,FFive months after her surgery at
OL,14,FSouthmead Hospital, Joanne says she
OL,15,Fhopes she will now be able to get back
OL,16,Fto work.
OL,18,F"I've set up a little podcast and some
OL,19,Fsocials to try and help people with
OL,20,Fendometriosis and adenomyosis and
OL,21,Fspread the word about it," she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
